    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、沙季も練習お疲れ様\nちょうど仕事の話をしたかったんだ。少しだけいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Saki‚ good job with the practice too.\nI wanted to talk about work. Can you spare a moment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです\nどんなお仕事ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nWhat kind of work is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "雑誌の特集で「アイドルの日常」という\n記事を組むことになったらしくてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems they want to feature an article\nin a magazine called \"Idols' Daily Lives.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、星見プロでも特に真面目な沙季なら「意外な\n一面があるかもしれないから」と声が掛かったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They thought that if it's you‚ Saki‚ who's particularly serious‚\nthere might be \"unexpected aspects\" they can capture.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "そういう理由で声が掛かることもあるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So they approached me with that kind of reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3733.333333400001,
          "startTime": 28.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと企画内容が……『仕事の時だけでなく\n休日の姿もなるべく等身大で伝えたい』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So the contents are…\n\"We want to convey your daily life as realistically as possible‚ not just during work hours.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "『そのため、関係者が写真を撮影したりメモを\n残したりして、それを基に記事を書く』……なるほど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"For that purpose‚ the staff will take photos and leave notes as they interact with you‚\nand then we will write the article based on that.\" I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_05_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "この場合の『関係者』というと……\n{user}さんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In this case‚ the \"staff\" would be\n… {user}-san‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}